ĽSTAN GORDON
1931-2005
From Poole. Dorset
"Just sit a while and enjoy
the sights and sounds of Padstow
he loved so much."
Remembered by his wife Wendy,
his family and close friends."¬
ŅRemembering our parents Derek and Mary Herbert
and the happy family holidays we all spent together

"Lark song and seasounds in the air
